# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  apps/web/.env  (copy to .env.local; gitignored)                         ║
# ╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║  Scope · Read by Vite at dev/build time and exposed to the SPA via       ║
# ║  `import.meta.env`. ONLY variables prefixed `VITE_` are bundled into     ║
# ║  browser code — everything else is ignored.                              ║
# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  Consumed by apps/web/src/lib/env.ts. Keep this surface minimal:         ║
# ║  anything placed here is PUBLIC the moment the bundle ships.             ║
# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  ⚠ Never put secrets here. Server runtime secrets belong in              ║
# ║    apps/server/.dev.vars or Cloudflare Worker secrets.                   ║
# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  ⚠ In production, inject these at build time                             ║
# ║    (e.g. `VITE_POSTHOG_KEY=... pnpm --filter @duedatehq/web build`).     ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

# Optional · Observability / Push public keys (all safe to expose in bundle)
VITE_POSTHOG_KEY=
VITE_SENTRY_DSN=
VITE_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=
